title: Jackie Cain & Roy Kral - Echoes (1976) Jazzed Media
description:
JACKIE CAIN & ROY KRAL - ECHOES

1. I Wonder What's The Matter With Me (Robert Ragan)
2. Corcovado (Antonio Calos Jobim - Gene Lees)
3. Mountain Greenery (Richard Rodgers - Lorenz Hart)
4. It's So Peaceful In The Country (Alec Wilder)
5. Walk Pretty (Alec Wilder - Fran Landesman)
6. Sweet Surrender (David Gates)
7. The Fat Man (Roy Kral - Fran Landesman)
8. How Little We Know (Hoagy Carmichael - Johnny Mercer)
9. The Way We Are (Roy Kral)
10. The Echoes Of My Life (Alec Wilder - Rodgers Brackett)
11. Samba Do Avio (Antonio Calos Jobim - Gene Lees)
12. Winter Comes (Harvie S - Jackie Cain)
13. The Runaround (Andre Previn - Dory Langdon)
14. Wheelers And Dealers (Dave Frishberg)
15. New York State Of Mind (Billy Joel)

Jackie Cain - vocals
Roy Kral - vocals & piano
John Mosher - bass
Gary Nash - drums
Brian Atkinson - vibes

Recorded in performance at Howard Rumsey's Concerts By The Sea, September 16-18, 1976

2007 Jazzed Media
